{"tid":611972,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家d朱古力奶真係好難飲","createTime":"2018-03-31T14:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T14:45:34.000Z","uid":162853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8afa56a56b99ebb28e6020a3f7705f6eb1c8aa49","tid":611972,"uid":162853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"講緊維他出嗰隻<br />\n廿年前第一次飲嗰陣真係有朱古力味 嗰陣一試難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自此好中意朱古力奶<br />\n後尾佢愈來愈唔好飲 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而家直頭得番甜味撈朱古力醬味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n好耐之前仲有出下薄荷朱古力味<br />\n當時好似都ok受歡迎<br />\n唔知有無人記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ooexITnZ6UY/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FooexITnZ6UY%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=cc702902&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a600cd6e133200174b07c7ac1d93b30a466c79db","tid":611972,"uid":162853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}